{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d58a6a0d59","title":"青化位战斗后准备打第二仗","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"53ff3eba47","index":0,"year":1947,"month":3,"day":26,"articleId":"d58a6a0d59"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b283d183f7","type":"paragraph","text":"青化位战斗后准备打第二仗”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"2a71c00206","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年3月26日）彭、习：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"d0f0042439","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）庆祝你们好灭三十一旅主力之胜利。此战意义甚大，望对全体指战员传令嘉奖。（二）一三五旅可能向青化砭方向寻找三十一旅，望准备打第二仗。（三）毛于昨日已与中央各同志会合","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"e8c65bfb3e","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"9a24d71be1","type":"paragraph","text":"寅有午[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给西北野战兵团司令员兼政治委员彭德怀和副政治委员习仲助的电报。1947年3月19日中共中央、中央军委主动撤出延安后，西北野战兵团以小部兵力诱敌主力进至安赛（在延安西北），主力理伏于延安东北的青化税地区，待机牙敌。3月25日，国民党军胡宗南部整编第二十七师第三十一旅旅部率1个团共2900余人进入西北野战兵团预伏圈内，经过一个多小时的战斗，被我全部开灭。[2]毛，指毛泽东。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"461b45d28e","type":"paragraph","text":"AAA九78免站快第（家>","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"cc7e5cd91b","type":"paragraph","text":"6区钢展叶旅力大","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"2a7ae1f025","type":"paragraph","text":"大智功金本植捷满升（嘉爽，）-=在放可的向系我体旅望锅和率）元我略目山后情表表同志含会。第生资有台","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"},{"id":"218141957e","type":"paragraph","text":"科识的前叶旅之肤们毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的致彭德怀、习仲勋电的手稿。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59"}],"page":{"id":"08557a083b","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"d58a6a0d59","start":469,"end":470}}}},"__N_SSG":true}